# Push to GitHub after changes

When a task edits files in this repository:

1. Run `git status` from the repo root; never commit `.env` or secrets.
2. `git add`, `git commit` with a clear message, and `git push origin main` (or the deployment branch) in the same session unless the user asks not to push.
